TITLE: Configure preset in babel.config.json
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration file shows how to include the @babel/preset-typescript preset in your Babel configuration.  It's the recommended way to configure Babel.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/preset-typescript.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "presets": ["@babel/preset-typescript"]
}
```

