TITLE: babel.config.json example for assumptions
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates using the enumerableModuleMeta assumption.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-modules-commonjs.md#_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: babel.config.json
CODE:
```
{
  "assumptions": {
    "enumerableModuleMeta": true
  }
}
```

