TITLE: Use Babel Plugin via Node API
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the Babel Node API to transform JavaScript code with the @babel/plugin-transform-object-rest-spread plugin. The transformSync method is used to synchronously transform the provided code string.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-object-rest-spread.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
require("@babel/core").transformSync("code", {
  plugins: ["@babel/plugin-transform-object-rest-spread"],
});
```

