TITLE: Babel Configuration with .babelrc.json
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the basic structure of a `.babelrc.json` file, which is used for file-relative Babel configurations. It shows the `presets` and `plugins` options, which are used to specify the transformations Babel should apply.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/configuration.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "presets": [...],
  "plugins": [...]
}
```

