TITLE: Configure Plugin in babel.config.json
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to configure the `@babel/plugin-transform-class-properties` plugin in the `babel.config.json` file, without any additional options. This enables the plugin to transform class properties in the project.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-class-properties.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "plugins": ["@babel/plugin-transform-class-properties"]
}
```

