TITLE: Install Babel plugin via npm/yarn
DESCRIPTION: This command installs the @babel/plugin-syntax-optional-chaining package as a development dependency using npm or yarn. This allows Babel to parse the optional chaining syntax.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-syntax-optional-chaining.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
npm install --save-dev @babel/plugin-syntax-optional-chaining
```

