TITLE: Usage via Node API JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the `@babel/core` package's `transformSync` method to transform code with the `@babel/plugin-transform-class-static-block` plugin within a Node.js environment.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-class-static-block.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
require("@babel/core").transformSync("code", {
  plugins: ["@babel/plugin-transform-class-static-block"],
});
```

