TITLE: Class Decorator with Parameter (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Shows a class decorator that takes a parameter and modifies the target class based on the parameter value. The `isTestable` function returns a decorator function that sets the `isTestable` property of the target class based on the provided `value`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-proposal-decorators.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
@isTestable(true)
class MyClass {}

function isTestable(value) {
  return function decorator(target) {
    target.isTestable = value;
  };
}
```

