TITLE: Configure importPolyfill option in babel.config.json
DESCRIPTION: Configures the `importPolyfill` option of the @babel/plugin-proposal-record-and-tuple plugin within a babel.config.json file. Setting importPolyfill to true imports the polyfill.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-proposal-record-and-tuple.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "plugins": [
    [
      "@babel/plugin-proposal-record-and-tuple",
      {
        "importPolyfill": true
      }
    ]
  ]
}
```

