TITLE: Babel Config: Plugin Usage - With Options
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration snippet shows how to enable the `@babel/plugin-transform-private-methods` plugin in a `babel.config.json` file with the `loose` option set to `true`. The 'loose' mode improves performance but may leak private members.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-private-methods.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "plugins": [["@babel/plugin-transform-private-methods", { "loose": true }]]
}
```

