TITLE: Install Babel Plugin (npm)
DESCRIPTION: Command to install the @babel/plugin-transform-react-jsx plugin as a development dependency using npm.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-react-jsx.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: Shell
CODE:
```
npm install --save-dev @babel/plugin-transform-react-jsx
```

