TITLE: Automatic Polyfilling Example
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code demonstrates how Babel, with the `useBuiltIns: "usage"` option, automatically injects polyfill imports based on the code's usage. This example imports `core-js/modules/es6.promise` because `Promise` is used.
