TITLE: Arrow Functions with Lexical `this` in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the use of arrow functions in ES2015, highlighting their concise syntax and lexical `this` binding. It showcases expression and statement bodies, as well as how arrow functions inherit the `this` context from their surrounding code and share the 'arguments' variable of the parent function.
