TITLE: ES2015 Parameters Example - Output JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This is the ES5 equivalent of the previous JavaScript code, generated by the @babel/plugin-transform-parameters plugin. It demonstrates how default, destructuring, and rest parameters are transformed to be compatible with older JavaScript environments. The output handles default values using ternary operators and array manipulation for rest parameters.
