TITLE: Transformed ES5 Class Example (Output)
DESCRIPTION: The output code generated by Babel when transforming the ES2015 class example. It demonstrates how the class is converted into ES5-compatible function and prototype-based code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-classes.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
function _classCallCheck(instance, Constructor) {
  if (!(instance instanceof Constructor)) {
    throw new TypeError("Cannot call a class as a function");
  }
}

var Test = (function() {
  function Test(name) {
    _classCallCheck(this, Test);

    this.name = name;
  }

  Test.prototype.logger = function logger() {
    console.log("Hello", this.name);
  };

  return Test;
})();
```

