TITLE: Arrow Function Transformation Example (Out)
DESCRIPTION: Shows the output JavaScript code after the arrow functions have been transformed into standard ES5 functions. This transformation ensures compatibility with older browsers or environments that don't natively support arrow functions. The `this` context is also handled appropriately.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-arrow-functions.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
