TITLE: Transform Class Static Block JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the transformation of a class with a static block into a static private property within an IIFE. The original class `C` has a static block that handles potential errors during the initialization of the static property `y`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-class-static-block.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
class C {
  static #x = 42;
  static y;
  static {
    try {
      this.y = doSomethingWith(this.#x);
    } catch {
      this.y = "unknown";
    }
  }
}
```

