SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-proposal-pipeline-operator.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// Status quo
jQuery.merge( this, jQuery.parseHTML(
  match[ 1 ],
  context && context.nodeType ? context.ownerDocument || context : document,
  true
) );

// With pipes
context
  |> (^^ && ^^.nodeType ? ^^.ownerDocument || ^^ : document)
  |> jQuery.parseHTML(match[1], ^^, true)
  |> jQuery.merge(^^);
```

