TITLE: JavaScript with bugfixes disabled
DESCRIPTION: Shows how Babel transforms JavaScript code with function parameters when targeting Edge 16, but with `bugfixes` option disabled. It demonstrates how the code is transformed to ES5-like parameters to avoid the bug.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/website/blog/2020-03-16-7.9.0.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
