TITLE: JSX Transformation with Runtime Helper
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how Babel transforms JSX with spread properties by default, injecting a runtime helper function `_extends`. The helper function merges the properties of the spread object into the element's attributes.  Requires `@babel/plugin-transform-react-jsx` or `@babel/preset-react`.
