TITLE: Transform for-of Loop with loose mode (Output)
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code is the result of transforming the for-of loop with the 'loose' option enabled.  It uses Array.isArray to determine if the iterable is an array and then uses a basic `for` loop for iteration, offering increased performance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/docs/plugin-transform-for-of.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
for (
  var _iterator = foo,
    _isArray = Array.isArray(_iterator),
    _i = 0,
    _iterator = _isArray ? _iterator : _iterator[Symbol.iterator]();
  ;

) {
  var _ref;

  if (_isArray) {
    if (_i >= _iterator.length) break;
    _ref = _iterator[_i++];
  } else {
    _i = _iterator.next();
    if (_i.done) break;
    _ref = _i.value;
  }

  var i = _ref;
}
```

