TITLE: Regenerator Runtime Helper Code Diff
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows the diff between old and new Babel versions when compiling a generator function. It highlights that, in Babel 7.18.0, `regenerator-runtime` is inlined, eliminating the need for a global `regeneratorRuntime` variable.
