TITLE: Class with private property check and static block in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code shows the use of private-property-in-object and class-static-block features in a JavaScript class. The `shippedProposals` option in `@babel/preset-env` now includes the plugins for these features, allowing them to be safely removed from the configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babel/website/blob/main/website/blog/2021-04-29-7.14.0.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
class Foo {
  #bar = "bar";

  test(obj) {
    return #bar in obj; // private-property-in-object
  }

  static #x = 42;
  static y;
  static { // static block
    try {
      this.y = doSomethingWith(this.#x);
    } catch {
      this.y = "unknown";
    }
  }
}
```

